<example id="exam-00001">
<title>Identifying the Acidic Hydrogens in a Compound</title>
<para id="para-00007">Identify the most acidic hydrogens in each of the following compounds, and rank the compounds in order of increasing acidity:</para>

<figure class="unnumbered scaled-down" id="fig-00005">
<media alt="Alt Text Placeholder">
